{"words":[{"word":"rover","count":6},{"word":"work","count":5},{"word":"thank","count":4},{"word":"time","count":3},{"word":"research","count":3},{"word":"continue","count":3},{"word":"tree","count":2},{"word":"woodveil","count":2},{"word":"hall","count":2},{"word":"data","count":2},{"word":"lab","count":2},{"word":"mission","count":2},{"word":"mt","count":2},{"word":"firmament","count":2},{"word":"day","count":2},{"word":"fantastic","count":1},{"word":"sight","count":1},{"word":"sure","count":1},{"word":"frequency","count":1},{"word":"faint","count":1},{"word":"analyzing","count":1},{"word":"appears","count":1},{"word":"prototype","count":1},{"word":"chronosorter","count":1},{"word":"positively","count":1},{"word":"impacted","count":1},{"word":"local","count":1},{"word":"ecology","count":1},{"word":"besides","count":1},{"word":"rewinding","count":1},{"word":"equipment","count":1},{"word":"designed","count":1},{"word":"seems","count":1},{"word":"accident","count":1},{"word":"caused","count":1},{"word":"unknown","count":1},{"word":"factors","count":1},{"word":"resurrect","count":1},{"word":"dead","count":1},{"word":"grant","count":1},{"word":"immortality","count":1},{"word":"living","count":1},{"word":"reverse","count":1},{"word":"natural","count":1},{"word":"cycle","count":1},{"word":"life","count":1},{"word":"pity","count":1},{"word":"creators","count":1},{"word":"witness","count":1},{"word":"yes","count":1},{"word":"memory","count":1},{"word":"corrupted","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"course","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"lost","count":1},{"word":"names","count":1},{"word":"since","count":1},{"word":"restored","count":1},{"word":"somehow","count":1},{"word":"behalf","count":1},{"word":"director","count":1},{"word":"prof","count":1},{"word":"bram","count":1},{"word":"junior","count":1},{"word":"researcher","count":1},{"word":"victor","count":1},{"word":"christopher","count":1},{"word":"thirty-three","count":1},{"word":"faculty","count":1},{"word":"members","count":1},{"word":"restoring","count":1},{"word":"despite","count":1},{"word":"failure","count":1},{"word":"given","count":1},{"word":"chance","count":1},{"word":"finish","count":1},{"word":"started","count":1},{"word":"whether","count":1},{"word":"takes","count":1},{"word":"century","count":1},{"word":"millennium","count":1},{"word":"victor's","count":1},{"word":"wish","count":1},{"word":"saying","count":1},{"word":"chronosorters","count":1},{"word":"save","count":1},{"word":"true","count":1},{"word":"paid","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"forgive","count":1},{"word":"feeling","count":1},{"word":"beyond","count":1},{"word":"capacity","count":1},{"word":"emotional","count":1},{"word":"module","count":1},{"word":"researchers","count":1},{"word":"grew","count":1},{"word":"doubtful","count":1},{"word":"thinking","count":1},{"word":"impossible","count":1},{"word":"stayed","count":1},{"word":"left","count":1},{"word":"world","count":1},{"word":"regret","count":1},{"word":"unfulfilled","count":1},{"word":"wishes","count":1},{"word":"becomes","count":1},{"word":"clear","count":1},{"word":"vain","count":1},{"word":"feel","count":1},{"word":"relieved","count":1},{"word":"learn","count":1},{"word":"telling","count":1},{"word":"maybe","count":1},{"word":"supreme","count":1},{"word":"authority","count":1},{"word":"hand","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"determine","count":1},{"word":"tasks","count":1},{"word":"going","count":1},{"word":"forward","count":1},{"word":"suggestion","count":1},{"word":"instruct","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"mysteries","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"remain","count":1},{"word":"unsolved","count":1},{"word":"confident","count":1},{"word":"uncover","count":1},{"word":"truth","count":1},{"word":"order","count":1},{"word":"received","count":1},{"word":"i'd","count":1},{"word":"observe","count":1},{"word":"bit","count":1},{"word":"longer","count":1},{"word":"began","count":1},{"word":"seed","count":1},{"word":"become","count":1},{"word":"shelter","count":1},{"word":"whole","count":1},{"word":"flies","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"What a fantastic sight, Rover. I'm sure the frequency of this tree was... faint until just now.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"Analyzing... It appears the Prototype Chronosorter has positively impacted the local ecology, besides rewinding the time for the equipment in Woodveil Hall.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"It wasn't designed for this. It seems more like an accident, caused by unknown factors.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"It didn't resurrect the dead or grant immortality to the living, but it did reverse what should be a natural cycle of life.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"It's a pity my creators aren't here to witness this.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"Yes, Rover. My memory data has been corrupted over a long course of time. I've even lost their names.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"But since you restored Woodveil Hall, the data has... somehow come back to me.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"I thank you on behalf of the Research Director Prof. Bram S., Junior Researcher Victor Christopher, and the other thirty-three faculty members.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"I thank you for restoring the Lab, despite the failure of their research. You have given me the chance to continue their work and finish what they started.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"Whether it takes a century or even a millennium... I will continue this work. It is my mission, and it is Victor's wish.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"So you're saying, the Chronosorters did save Mt. Firmament. Is that true, Rover?","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"So it all paid off... Please forgive me Rover, what I'm feeling right now is beyond the capacity of my emotional module.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"Some of the researchers... grew doubtful of their work, thinking it was mission impossible.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"While those who stayed left this world with regret and unfulfilled wishes.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"Now it becomes all clear... Their work wasn't in vain. They would feel relieved too, if they were to learn this.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"Thank you Rover, for telling me all this.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"Maybe... With the supreme authority in hand, you are now in the place to determine my tasks going forward.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"Suggestion: You may instruct me to continue the research here. Many mysteries around Mt. Firmament remain unsolved. I'm confident we'll uncover the truth one day.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"Order received... Thank you.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"I'd like to observe this tree for a bit longer, Rover. My work began the day it was just a seed.","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000},{"text":"And now... it has become the shelter of the whole Lab. How time flies...","quest_name":"Vigil of Endless Night","quest_id":143000000}]}